      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST INCREDIBLE (5) resumes after great success last prep, winning on two occasions and culminating in a tenth over 2240m at Melton on November 15. Well-placed against this line-up. IMA CHARMA (1) made it two wins from the past five outings at his latest appearance over 1680m at Terang, scoring by 7 metres after taking the lead a fair way from home. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and rates a leading hope in a similar race. THE VILLAIN (2) must be considered after he finished runner-up over 1609m at this track five days ago. OLLIES MEDAL (7) is in the mix following a respectable third at his most recent appearance over 2190m at Shepparton.",
